hadiths[15]{hadithnumber,text}:
334,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath kuchh safar ( jang bani mustaliq) mein they. jab ham maqam beda ya zaat-al-Jaish par pahunchey to mera aik haar kho gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uski talash mein wahin thahar gaey aur log bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath thahar gaey. lekin wahan pani kahin qareeb mein na tha. log Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur kaha '' Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kya kaam kya? ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur tamam logon ko thehra diya hai aur pani bhi kahin qareeb mein nahi hai aur na logon hi ke sath hai.'' phir Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laaey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apna sar Mubarak meri raan par rakhey huey so rahe they. farmaney lagey ke tum ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur tamam logon ko rok liya. halanke qareeb mein kahin pani bhi nahi hai aur na logon ke paas hai. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke walid maajid (Raziallahu anhu) mujh par bahut khafa huey aur Allah ne jo chaha unhon-ne mujhey kaha aur apne hath se meri kokh mein kachokey lagaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka sar Mubarak meri raan par tha. us wjah se main harkat bhi nahi kar sakti thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab subah ke waqt uthey to pani ka pata tak na tha. to Allah Taala ne tayammum ki aayat utari aur logon ne tayammum kya. is par Usaid-bin-Huzair (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ''aey aale-abi-Bakar ! ye tumhari koi pehli barkat nahi hai.'' Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya, phir ham ne us oont ko hataya jis par main sawar thi to haar usi ke nichey mil gaya."
335,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya mujhey panch cheezein aisi di gaee hain jo mujh se pahley kisi ko nahi di gaee thin. aik maheene ki masafat se raub ke zariey meri madad ki gaee hai aur tamam zameen mere liye sajdagaah aur paakii ke laaiq banai gaee. to meri ummat ka jo insan Namaz ke waqt ko) jahan bhi) paa-ley usey wahan hi Namaz ada kar leni chahiye aur mere liye ghaneemat ka maal halal kya gaya hai. mujh se pahley ye kisi ke liye bhi halal na tha aur mujhey shafaat ata ki gaee aur tamam anbiya apni apni qaum ke liye maboos hotey they lekin main tamam insanon ke liye aam taur par Nabi bana kar bheja gaya hun.
336,"unhon-ne Asma (Raziallahu anha) se haar maang kar pahan liya tha, wo gum ho gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aadmi ko uski talash ke liye bheja , jisey wo mil gaya. phir Namaz ka waqt aa pahuncha aur logon ke paas (jo haar ki talash mein gaey they) pani nahi tha. logon ne Namaz padh li aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske mutaalliq shikayat ki. to Allah tabarak w taala ne tayammum ki aayat utari jisey sun kar Usaid-bin-Huzair ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se kaha aapko Allah behtreen badla de. Allah ki qism jab bhi aap ke sath koi aisi baat pesh aai jis se aapko takleef hui to Allah Taala ne aap ke liye aur tamam musalmanon ke liye usmein khair paida farma di."
337,"main aur Abdullah-bin Yasar jo ke Memuna (Raziallahu anha) bevi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghulam they, abu-Jaheem bin-Haaris bin Simma Ansari ( sahabi (ke paas aaey. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ''biare-jamal'' ki taraf se tashrif la rahe they, rastey mein aik shakhs ne aapko salam kya (yani khud usi abu-Jaheem ne) lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jawab nahi diya. phir aap diwar ke qareeb aaey aur apne chehrey aur hathon ka masah kya phir unke salam ka jawab diya."
338,"aik shakhs umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur kaha ke mujhey ghusl ki haajat ho gaee aur pani nahi mila (to mein ab kya karun ( is par Ammar bin-Yaasir (Raziallahu anhu) ne umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha, kya aapko yad nahi jab main aur aap safar mein they, ham donon junbi (hambistari k baad ki napaki ki haalat me) ho gaey. aap ne to Namaz nahi padhi lekin maine zameen par lot-pot liya, aur Namaz padh li. phir maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska zikr kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tujhey bas itna hi kafi tha aur aap ne apne donon hath zameen par maarey phir unhein phoonka aur donon se chehrey aur pahunchon ka masah kya."
339,"ye waqia bayan kya (jo pahley guzar chuka (aur Shoba ne apne hathon ko zameen par maaraa. phir unhein apne munh ke qareeb kar liya (aur phoonkaa ( phir unse apne chehrey aur pohnchon ka masah kya aur Nazar-bin-Shumail ne bayan kya ke mujhey Shoba ne khabar di hukm se ke maine-Zar-bin-Abdullaah se suna, wo Saeed-bin-Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Abzaa ke hawale se hadis riwayat kartey they. Hakam ne kaha ke maine ye hadis ibne- Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Abza se suni , wo apne walid ke hawale se bayan kartey they ke Ammar ne kaha (jo pahley mazkoor hua)."
340,"wo umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir they aur Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha ke ham aik lashkar mein gaey huey they. to ham donon junbi (hambistari k baad ki napaki ki haalat me) ho gaey aur (is mein hai ke bajaey ( نفخ فيهما‏ ( ke) unhon-ne ( تفل فيهما‏ ( kaha,"
341,main to zameen mein lot-pot ho gaya phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke terey liye sirf chehrey aur Pohnchon par masah karna kafi tha ( zameen par letney ki zarurat na thi).
342,"mein umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein maujood tha ke Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha, phir unhon-ne poori hadis bayan ki."
343,to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hathon ko zameen par maara aur us se apne chehrey aur Pohnchon ka masah kya
344,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik safar mein they ke ham raat bhar chaltey rahe aur jab raat ka aakhiri hissey aaya to ham ne padao daala aur musaafir ke liye us waqt ke padao se zyada marghoob aur koi cheez nahi hoti ( phir ham is tarah ghaafil ho kar so gaey (ke hamein suraj ki garmi ke siwa koi cheez bedaar na kar sakii. sabse pahley bedaar honey wala shakhs falan tha. phir falan phir fulaan. abu-Rijaa ne sab ke naam liye lekin Auf ko ye naam yad nahi rahe. phir chauthey number par jaagney waley umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) they aur jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aaraam farmatey to ham aapko jagaatey nahi they. yahan tak ke aap khud-b-khud bedaar hun. kyonke hamein kuchh malum nahi hota ke aap par khuwab mein kya taaza wahi aati hai. jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) jaag gaey aur ye aafat aati hui dekhi aur wo aik nidar dil waley aadmi they. to zor-zor se takbeer kehney lagey. isi tarah buland awaz mein, aap us waqt tak takbeer kehtey rahe jab tak ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unki awaz se bedaar na ho gaey. to logon ne pesh aanewaalii museebat ke mutaalliq Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se shikayat ki. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke koi haraj nahi. safar shuru karo. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) thodi door chaley, iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) thahar gaey aur wuzu ka pani talab farmaya aur wuzu kya aur azan kahi gaee. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ke sath Namaz padhi. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padhaaney se farigh huey to aik shakhs par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nazar padi jo alag kinarey par khada hua tha aur usne logon ke sath Namaz nahi padhi thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usse farmaya ke aey fulaan! tumhen logon ke sath Namaz mein Sharik honey se kon si cheez ne rokaa. usne jawab diya ke mujhey ghusl ki haajat ho gaee aur pani maujood nahi hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke paak mitti se kaam nikaal lo. yahi tujh ko kafi hai. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne safar shuru kya to logon ne piyaas ki shikayat ki. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) thahar gaey aur falan (yani Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu)) ko bulaya. abu-Rijaa ne unka naam liya tha lekin Auf ko yad nahi raha aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi talab farmaya, un donon se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jao pani talash karo. ye donon nikley. rasta mein aik aurat mili jo pani ki 2 pakhaalein apne oont par latkaey huey beech mein Sawar ho kar ja rahi thi. unhon-ne usse puchha ke pani kahan milta hai? to usne jawab diya ke kal isi waqt mein pani par maujood thi (yani pani itni door hai ke kal mein isi waqt wahan se pani lekar chali thi aaj yahan pahunchi hon) aur hamarey qabeele ke mard log peechhey reh gaey hain. unhon-ne usse kaha, achchha hamarey sath chalo. usne poochha, kahan chalun? unhon-ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein. usne kaha, achchha wahi jinko log saabi kehtey hain. unhon-ne kaha, ye wahi hain, jisey tum keh rahi ho. achchha ab chalo. aakhir ye donon hazraat us aurat ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat Mubarak mein laey aur Sara waqia bayan kya. Imran ne kaha ke logon ne usey oont se utaar liya. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik bartan talab farmaya aur donon pakhaalon ya mishkezon ke munh us bartan mein khol diye. phir unka uper ka munh band kar diya. iske baad nichey ka munh khol diya aur tamam lashkariyon mein manaadii kar di gaee ke khud bhi sair ho kar pani piein aur apne tamam janwaron wghaira ko bhi pilaa lein. to jisne chaha pani piyaa aur pilaya (aur sab sair ho gaey ( aakhir mein us shakhs ko bhi aik bartan mein pani diya jisey ghusl ki zarurat thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ley ja aur ghusl kar ley. wo aurat khadi dekh rahi thi ke iske pani se kya kya kaam liye ja rahe hain aur Allah ki qism ! jab pani liya jana unse band hua, to ham dekh rahe they ke ab mishkezon mein pani pahley se bhi zyada maujood tha. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kuchh uske liye ( khaney ki cheez ( jama karo. logon ne uske liye umda qism ki khajoor (ajwa) aata aur sattu ikattha kya. yahan tak ke bahut Sara khana uske liye jama ho gaya. to usey logon ne aik kapdey mein rakha aur aurat ko oont par Sawar karke uske samney wo kapda rakh diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya ke tumhen malum hai ke ham ne tumharey pani mein koi kami nahi ki hai. lekin Allah Taala ne hamein sairaab kar diya. phir wo apne ghar aai , der kafi ho chuki thi isliye ghar walon ne puchha ke aey fulaanii ! kyon itni der huii? usne kaha, aik ajeeb baat hui wo ye ke mujhey 2 aadmi miley aur wo mujhey us shakhs ke paas le gaey jisey log saabi kehtey hain. wahan is tarah ka waqia pesh aaya, Allah ki qism ! wo to iske aur uske darmyan sabse bada jadoo gar hai aur us ne beech ki ungli aur shahadat ki ungli aasman ki taraf utha kar ishara kya. uski murad aasman aur zameen se thi. ya phir wo waqei Allah ka rasool hai. iske baad musalman us qabeele ke door w nazdeek ke mushrekeen par hamley kya kartey they. lekin us gharaaney ko jis se us aurat ka talluq tha koi nuqsan nahi pahunchaatey they. ye achchha bartaw dekh kar aik din us aurat ne apni qaum se kaha ke mera khayal hai ke ye log tumhen jaan-bojh kar chhod detey hain. to kya tumhen Islam ki taraf kuchh raghbat hai? qaum ne aurat ki baat maan li aur Islam ley aai. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne farmaya ke) sabaa (ke mana hain apna Deen chhod kar doosrey ke Deen mein chala gaya aur abul-Aaliyaa ne kaha hai ke Sabein ahle-kitab ka aik firqa hai jo Zabur padhtey hain aur sura Yusuf mein jo ( اصب (ka lafz hai wahan bhi iske mana ( امل (ke hain."
345,"agar (ghusl ki haajat ho aur) pani na miley to kya Namaz na padhi jaey. Abdullah ne farmaya, haan! agar mujhey aik mahina tak bhi pani na miley to main Namaz na padhunga. agar usmein logon ko ijazat de di jaey to sardi malum karke bhi log tayammum se Namaz padh lengey. abu-Musa kehtey hain ke maine kaha ke phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke samney Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ke qaul ka kya jawab hoga. boley ke mujhey to nahi malum hai ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ki baat se mut'ma'in ho gaey they."
346,"mein Abdullah ( Abdullah-bin-Masood (aur abu-Musa Ash-ari ki khidmat mein tha, abu-Musa ne puchha ke abu-Abdur-Rehman ! aap ka kya khayal hai ke agar kisi ko ghusl ki haajat ho aur pani na miley to wo kya kare. Abdullah ne farmaya ke usey Namaz na padhni chahiye jab tak usey pani na mil jaey. abu-Musa ne kaha ke phir Ammar ki is riwayat ka kya hoga jabke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse kaha tha ke tumhen sirf ( hath aur munh ka tayammum ( kafi tha. ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke tum umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko nahi dekhtey ke wo Ammar ki is baat par mut'm'in nahi huey they. phir abu-Musa ne kaha ke achchha Ammar ki baat ko chhodo lekin us aayat ka kya jawab doge (jis mein janabat mein tayammum karne ki waazeh ijazat maujood hai) Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) iska koi jawab na de sakey. sirf ye kaha ke agar ham uski bhi logon ko ijazat de dein to unka haal ye ho jaeyga ke agar kisi ko pani thanda malum hua to usey chhod diya karega aur tayammum kar liya karega . (Aamash kehtey hain ke) maine Shaqiq se kaha ke maano Abdullah ne us wjah se ye sura na-pasand ki thi. to unhon-ne jawab diya ke haan."
347,"agar aik shakhs ko ghusl ki haajat ho aur mahina bhar pani na paaey to kya wo tayammum karke Namaz na padhey ? Shaqiq kehtey hain ke Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya ke wo tayammum na karey agarche wo aik mahina tak pani na paaey (aur Namaz moquf rakhey ( abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par kaha ke phir sura Mayeda ki us aayat ka kya matlab hoga ''agar tum pani na paogey to paak mitti par tayammum kar lo. '' Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) boley ke agar logon ko uski ijazat de di jaey to jald hi ye haal ho jaeyga ke jab unko pani thanda malum hoga to wo mitti se tayammum hi kar lengey. Aamash ne kaha maine Shaqiq se kaha to tum ne junbi (hambistari k baad ki napaki ki haalat me) ke liye tayammum isliye bura jaanaa. unhon-ne kaha haan. phir abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke kya aapko Ammar ka Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke samney ye qaul malum nahi ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi kaam ke liye bheja tha. safar mein mujhey ghusl ki zarurat ho gaee, lekin pani na mila. isliye main mitti mein janwar ki tarah lot-pot liya. phir maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska zikr kya. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumharey liye sirf itna karna kafi tha aur aap ne apne hathon ko zameen par aik martaba maara phir unko jhaad kar baain hath se daahiney ki pusht ko mal liya ya baain hath ka daahiney hath se masah kya. phir donon hathon se chehrey ka masah kya. Abdullah ne iska jawab diya ke aap umr ko nahi dekhtey ke unhon-ne Ammar ki baat par qanaa'at nahi ki thi aur Ya'laa-ibn-Ubaid ne Aamash ke waaste se Shaqiq se riwayat mein ye zyadti ki hai ke unhon-ne kaha ke main Abdullah aur abu-Musa ki khidmat mein tha aur abu-Musa ne farmaya tha ke aap ne umr se Ammar ka ye qaul nahi suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey aur aapko bhejaa. to mujhey ghusl ki haajat ho gaee aur main mitti mein lot-pot liya. phir main raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se soorate-haal ke mutaalliq zikr kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhen sirf itna hi kafi tha aur apne chehrey aur hatheliyon ka aik hi martaba masah kya."
348,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aadmi ko dekha ke alag khada hua hai aur logon ke sath Namaz mein Sharik nahi ho raha hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey falan ! tumhen logon ke sath Namaz padhney se kis cheez ne rok diya. usne kaha ya Rasulullah ! mujhey ghusl ki zarurat ho gaee aur pani nahi hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya phir tum ko paak mitti se tayammum karna zaroori tha, bas wo tumharey liye kafi hotaa."
